    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily driver. The engine and transmission are fully operational, though buyers should expect the standard wear and tear associated with its age, including some minor fluid seeps and suspension noise over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows visible wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid, functional car that would benefit from some cosmetic TLC and routine maintenance to bring it back to its best.",
