    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline via six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with an M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates, addressing the chassis's known stress points. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and lateral stability expected of the M-chassis. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity is robust, with recent rod bearing service and valve adjustment completed. A visceral, analog machine ready for the enthusiast who values engineering and mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Interior is clean. Mechanically sound. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that exemplifies pride of ownership. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss luster, showing only the expected minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood from highway travel. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with ample tread remaining. Inside, the interior remains smoke-free and crisp; the bolsters on the driver's seat show minimal wear, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All power accessories, including the sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean, reflecting a history of regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The vehicle tracks straight, brakes firmly without pulsation, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a dependable, high-quality car that bridges the gap between everyday utility and premium comfort.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and roadworthiness. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, this offering represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a sophisticated balance of value and long-term reliability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a champ, making it perfect for your daily commute or fun weekend adventures. It's in really solid shape and is totally ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve priced it to move because I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy hand-off to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with proactive subframe reinforcement and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal timing and torque delivery. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-enjoyed machine, the mechanical vitals remain stout, featuring a refreshed cooling system and bushings that maintain the platform's signature handling dynamics and communicative steering feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
